340
00:25:32,887 --> 00:25:36,288
So he wants to see me.
Then she walks away.

341
00:25:36,357 --> 00:25:39,690
He figured you were gonna chicken
and never-- Impressive.

342
00:25:42,430 --> 00:25:44,364
Kinda out of it.

343
00:25:45,433 --> 00:25:47,663
I had to go to work last year.

344
00:25:47,735 --> 00:25:49,669
You still move it.

345
00:25:49,737 --> 00:25:54,572
You better watch that. Ariel's gonna
tell her pop and you're gonna burn.

346
00:25:54,642 --> 00:25:58,703
What's her story?
Is she really tough or what?

347
00:25:58,779 --> 00:26:01,839
She's just trying to make people
forget she's a preacher's kid.

348
00:26:04,151 --> 00:26:06,210
- That why she hangs out with Chuck?
- Maybe.

349
00:26:06,287 --> 00:26:09,916
- People think she's a hell-raiser.
- Is she?

350
00:26:09,991 --> 00:26:12,016
I think she's been kissed a lot.

351
00:26:18,933 --> 00:26:21,595
You'd never guess
your daddy's a fire chief.

352
00:26:21,669 --> 00:26:25,537
