a minister. Red Boots.

353
00:26:25,606 --> 00:26:28,632
My daddy hates me
wearing these boots.

354
00:26:28,709 --> 00:26:31,940
And you love that, don't you?

355
00:26:38,319 --> 00:26:40,879
What are you gonna do
when I go away to college?

356
00:26:40,955 --> 00:26:42,946
Why do you wanna do that, honey?

357
00:26:43,024 --> 00:26:46,858
Just 'cause. I'm cut out for more
than this small town.

358
00:26:48,029 --> 00:26:50,156
You're as small town
as they come.

359
00:27:02,943 --> 00:27:05,935
A chicken race with tractors?

360
00:27:07,548 --> 00:27:10,278
- How hard could it be?
-Just like a car. It's easy.

361
00:27:10,351 --> 00:27:13,787
Just like driving a sports car.
Nothing could be simpler.

362
00:27:13,854 --> 00:27:16,482
Oh, hell, Ren,
just remember to stay calm.

363
00:27:16,557 --> 00:27:19,822
