372
00:27:48,789 --> 00:27:50,723
You had a lot to smoke.

373
00:27:50,791 --> 00:27:52,850
Don't tell me
I had enough to smoke.

374
00:27:52,927 --> 00:27:55,896
I didn't say you had enough.
I said you had a lot to smoke.

375
00:27:55,963 --> 00:27:57,988
Don't tell me that either!

376
00:27:59,667 --> 00:28:03,125
