386
00:29:25,152 --> 00:29:27,780
- Come on, Ren!
- Go! Go!

387
00:29:39,813 --> 00:29:42,304
Let's see what you're made of!

388
00:29:46,286 --> 00:29:47,878
Come on, sucker!

389
00:29:51,325 --> 00:29:52,849
Chuck, move it!

390
00:30:01,001 --> 00:30:03,799
You wanna go up, huh?

391
00:30:03,870 --> 00:30:05,303
