392
00:30:09,643 --> 00:30:12,407
Oh, you wanna go down.

393
00:30:14,681 --> 00:30:16,581
Kick his ass!

394
00:30:25,258 --> 00:30:27,419
That's it!Jump, you chicken!

395
00:30:27,494 --> 00:30:29,052
Sit down!

396
00:30:38,839 --> 00:30:42,400
