397
00:30:42,476 --> 00:30:44,444
You stupid idiot!

398
00:30:44,511 --> 00:30:46,103
Get off!

399
00:30:46,179 --> 00:30:47,703
Turn out!

400
00:30:47,781 --> 00:30:49,749
Oh, shit!

401
00:31:17,310 --> 00:31:21,337
Help! He tried to kill me.

402
00:31:33,293 --> 00:31:35,761
Excuse me. Thank you.

403
00:31:38,532 --> 00:31:40,523
I don't believe this town.

404
00:31:42,536 --> 00:31:43,969
