405
00:31:45,205 --> 00:31:46,900
Tell me.

406
00:31:46,973 --> 00:31:49,373
He has team practice
every day until 4:00.

407
00:31:49,443 --> 00:31:53,504
Mondays, Wednesdays and Thursdays
he's at the Beamis Mill till 6:00.

408
00:31:53,580 --> 00:31:56,208
