461
00:38:43,723 --> 00:38:46,556
He likes to act like he does,
but he doesn't.

462
00:38:49,996 --> 00:38:52,556
Do you wanna kiss me?

463
00:38:53,366 --> 00:38:55,391
Someday.

464
00:38:57,437 --> 00:38:59,735
What is this someday shit?

465
00:39:01,741 --> 00:39:04,073
I get the feeling
you've been kissed a lot.

466
00:39:04,143 --> 00:39:07,237
I'm afraid I'd suffer
by comparison.

467
00:39:13,086 --> 00:39:15,247
You don't think much
of me, do you?

468
00:39:17,357 --> 00:39:19,450
You think I'm small town?

469
00:39:21,895 --> 00:39:23,829
I think Bomont's a small town.

470
00:39:26,466 --> 00:39:28,161
I'm going away.

471
00:39:29,402 --> 00:39:31,734
I've already applied to colleges.

472
00:39:31,804 --> 00:39:35,467
