doesn't know I applied to.

473
00:39:37,610 --> 00:39:41,102
He's gonna come after me,
but I'm gonna be gone.

474
00:39:55,328 --> 00:39:57,489
Wanna see something?

475
00:39:59,766 --> 00:40:01,358
Sure.

476
00:40:05,605 --> 00:40:08,335
We call it ''The Yearbook.''

477
00:40:08,408 --> 00:40:12,242
It started four or
five years ago, I guess.

478
00:40:12,312 --> 00:40:14,473
It's stuff we're not
supposed to read.

479
00:40:21,087 --> 00:40:23,055
This is all out of books?

480
00:40:23,122 --> 00:40:26,956
