486
00:40:49,816 --> 00:40:51,511
It's all right.

487
00:40:58,691 --> 00:41:01,626
Wait a minute.
You hear that?

488
00:41:01,694 --> 00:41:03,685
- What?
- The train. You hear it?

489
00:41:07,533 --> 00:41:10,730
Sometimes after football games
we come out here.

490
00:41:10,803 --> 00:41:14,432
Just a few of us.
And we stand here.

491
00:41:14,507 --> 00:41:18,204
Then when the train comes,
we make out like crazy.

492
00:41:19,412 --> 00:41:20,845
Oh, yeah?

493
00:41:23,149 --> 00:41:25,845
Most of the time
